               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240916-5-cd25" type="crimeDate">21st of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-5-off24 t18240916-5-cd25"></join>, at <placeName id="t18240916-5-crimeloc26">St. Botolph without, Aldersgate</placeName>
